dc_title_s: Plan of Detroit, 1830 by John Mullett.
dc_description_s: Cadastral map. Oriented with north toward the upper right. From American State papers. Public lands. Washington: Gales & Seaton, 1860. v. 6. "Vol. VI, PL-No. 900b." Includes index of buildings. 1 map; 45 x 36 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
